<p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;"><font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><b>When mom is happy, the whole family is happy. Ensure she is always happy &amp; healthy.</b></span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;">My dad used to repeat this to me and my brother ever since i remember. I never thought much about it until I realized how true that really is.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;">When our mother met with a road accident in 2005 skyline of our whole world crumbled. She suffered severe head injury which badly affected her eye sight. Life threw some dramatic changes in those 2 horrible months.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;">One fine day while still recovering, mom came out of her bedroom for the first time in 2 months. She almost fainted seeing the messy house &amp; untidy kitchen. Despite her illness she started bashing the father-daughter-son trinity for the damage caused to her home and that was the first time in 2 months a smile emerged on our face.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;">That was the first time i loved executing the orders my mom gave.</span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;">That is when i realized how important is a mother's health &amp; happiness are to a family. Since then my mom's well being comes as my first priority.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><b>When mom is happy, everyone is happy :)</b></span></font></p><p class="qtext_para" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;"><font color="#333333" face="Georgia, Times, Times New Roman, serif"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><a href="https://www.quora.com/What-is-the-best-advice-your-father-ever-gave-you/answer/Sharmila-Ashraf-1?srid=uLaia" target="_blank">Link</a></span></font></p>
